# Task Management with todo.md

- For each task, break it down into detailed, step-by-step items in `[todo.md](mdc:todo.md)`.
- Treat `[todo.md](mdc:todo.md)` as a live scratchpad.
- Update `[todo.md](mdc:todo.md)` continuously.
- Check off completed steps in `[todo.md](mdc:todo.md)`.
